snippet: Britain's Jamie Murray and Brazil's Bruno Soares will end the year as the top-ranked doubles duo after French pair Nicolas Mahut and Pierre-Hugues Herbert lost at the ATP World Tour Finals on Friday....
lead_paragraph: Britain's Jamie Murray and Brazil's Bruno Soares will end the year as the top-ranked doubles duo after French pair Nicolas Mahut and Pierre-Hugues Herbert lost at the ATP World Tour Finals on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Murray and Soares Clinch Year-End Top Doubles Ranking
headline.main: Murray and Soares Clinch Year-End Top Doubles Ranking
